node.text: My dear old friend surprised her mom with tickets to my show at The Ryman and I am all teared up!  Means the world to share such a big moment with you all!  Thanks, @kat12birdy ! X
Today, I mean business !
I love this show so much!  Aidy is so empowering!  I laugh and cry and relate - it’s so good!  @aidybryant @shrillhulu #catchingup
Thank you @colbertlateshow for having @NorahJones and me on your show! It was an honor!!!! You can watch it in full again at the link in my story!
Hard to believe how long it’s been since I’ve written this song. How much has happened. It still stirs my former and future self.
Tonight and tomorrow!  Beyond thrilled !!!
Someone stole my friend’s dog!  I’ve known Soybean for so long!!! Such a sweet dog!  Please be on the lookout, Angelenos!  X

I can’t stop thinking about this film.  You’ve done it again, Noah.  Incredible performances by Scarlett Johansson & Adam Driver & of course Laura Dern & Alan Alda... Tearing up now just thinking about #marriagestory
@mirandajuly @margaretqualley
What?! My performance on @colbertlateshow with @NorahJones airs tomorrow!! Our first time performing our version of 'Seventeen' on the TV! Thanks @AmazonMusic.
@mirandajuly

I recorded a special version of "Silent Night" for Eric Paschal Johnson's film The Letter, and I'm so happy to share it with you on its own for the first time! Listen on @AmazonMusic (link in bio). And a bonus - me on an ornament ca 4th grade! 🎄
Happy holidays, everyone!  20% off select merch in my store.  Some new items to check out too ! link in my story
Finding solace today.  Thank you, @thisispattismith xo

@JeffGoldblum & the Mildred Snitzer Orchestra and I got to sing our song on @JimmyKimmelLive last night. They are a true dream to sing with. Special thanks to @d_i_a_n_n_a___l_u_n_t for styling and @TheVampiresWife for the incredible dress. 
Watch at link in my story! X

My spring tour is on sale now! Tickets at sharonvanetten.com/tour. 
See you in April xo

I'm going on tour in the spring to some of my favorite cities in the southeast! @jaysomband will be joining me for all dates and @julienrbaker will be opening for a special show at The Ryman in Nashville. 
Tickets will be on sale tomorrow with code SEVENTEEN. Can't wait to see you soon.

I couldn’t think of a better way to make it back east for the holidays than to stop by and support @Wilco in their hometown of Chicago for a rare solo acoustic set. This is going to be a special couple of nights.
Happy Sunday ! #nytimescinnamonrolls @nytimes
That was a great first, proper Halloween, Los Angeles.  Thank you to all my new mom friends that have taken me under their wing.  So grateful.  X photo by @atsutagram

So proud of my friend and bandmate @devilhoof for releasing his music into the world.  It’s such a vulnerable thing to do.  Check out ‘Baile as Baile’ now on @spotify or @applemusic - really beautiful arrangements... X
@MosaWild covered my song “Comeback Kid” and it's so good! Means so much they connected to this song in their own way. Check out the whole thing at the link in my story. X
These shirts were such a hit on the Bon Iver tour we decided to make some more! A timeless message and mantra dear to my heart. Link in story to get yours x
It’s been almost ten years since I played @TinyDesk. It is comforting to see how much we all have grown. Thank you for having me, @nprmusic. Your support means so much to me. X
